"specialize","count":1},{"word":"words","count":1},{"word":"inflict","count":1},{"word":"emotional","count":1},{"word":"damage","count":1},{"word":"playername","count":1},{"word":"apologies","count":1},{"word":"usually","count":1},{"word":"coffee","count":1},{"word":"machines","count":1},{"word":"phonographs","count":1},{"word":"give","count":1},{"word":"second","count":1},{"word":"colleague","count":1},{"word":"found","count":1},{"word":"address","count":1},{"word":"residence","count":1},{"word":"journalist's","count":1},{"word":"hidden","count":1},{"word":"ability","count":1},{"word":"trade","count":1},{"word":"secret","count":1},{"word":"anyway","count":1},{"word":"visit","count":1},{"word":"ms","count":1},{"word":"strozzia's","count":1},{"word":"waste","count":1},{"word":"any","count":1},{"word":"aria","count":1},{"word":"mummer","count":1},{"word":"nexus","count":1},{"word":"following","count":1},{"word":"orders","count":1},{"word":"master","count":1},{"word":"acted","count":1},{"word":"traveling","count":1},{"word":"deliveries","count":1},{"word":"remarkable","count":1},{"word":"wonder","count":1},{"word":"really","count":1},{"word":"feelings","count":1},{"word":"blessed","count":1},{"word":"maiden","count":1},{"word":"grew","count":1},{"word":"worried","count":1},{"word":"corrupted","count":1},{"word":"dark","count":1},{"word":"tide","count":1},{"word":"thought","count":1},{"word":"abandoned","count":1},{"word":"masters","count":1},{"word":"yet","count":1},{"word":"traveled","count":1},{"word":"farthest","count":1},{"word":"islands","count":1},{"word":"saying","count":1},{"word":"believe","count":1},{"word":"story","count":1},{"word":"seen","count":1},{"word":"talking","count":1},{"word":"eyes","count":1},{"word":"suddenly","count":1},{"word":"feeling","count":1},{"word":"vast","count":1},{"word":"world","count":1},{"word":"corner","count":1},{"word":"infinite","count":1},{"word":"universe","count":1},{"word":"planning","count":1},{"word":"write","count":1},{"word":"team","count":1},{"word":"course","count":1},{"word":"better","count":1},{"word":"promised","count":1},{"word":"great","count":1},{"word":"male","count":1},{"word":"female","count":1},{"word":"word","count":1},{"word":"done","count":1},{"word":"work","count":1},{"word":"next","count":1},{"word":"fit","count":1},{"word":"schedule","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"Hello there! It's been a while!","quest_name":"Mummer's Wish","quest_id":119800000},{"text":"Haha, didn't expect the Laureate to still remember me after our short encounter.","quest_name":"Mummer's Wish","quest_id":119800000},{"text":"It's understandable if you don't remember me. It was a short encounter after all.","quest_name":"Mummer's Wish","quest_id":119800000},{"text":"Back in Maroonwood, I was busy encouraging those two young Gladiators into a friendly duel. Didn't notice it was you passing by until it was too late.","quest_name":"Mummer's Wish","quest_id":119800000},{"text":"Guess I'm lucky to bump into you again today. Otherwise, I'd have lived the rest of my life with regret.","quest_name":"Mummer's Wish","quest_id":119800000},{"text":"Right. I'm not sure why you'd go through all this trouble helping an Echo, but you're stuck and need clues, yes?","quest_name":"Mummer's Wish","quest_id":119800000},{"text":"Not many Septimontians recognize these sigils… Except me, that is. I can help you in exchange for a tiny favor.","quest_name":"Mummer's Wish","quest_id":119800000},{"text":"Relax, it's nothing over-the-top. An exclusive interview with you will do.","quest_name":"Mummer's Wish","quest_id":119800000},{"text":"I won't take too much of your time, and we can do the interview after solving your Echo problem first. How's that sound?","quest_name":"Mummer's Wish","quest_id":119800000},{"text":"Decisive! As expected from the Champion and Laureate!","quest_name":"Mummer's Wish","quest_id":119800000},{"text":"By all means. I'll make sure to book the quietest room in the fanciest hotel in Septimont for our interview.","quest_name":"Mummer's Wish","quest_id":119800000},{"text":"Alright, let's take care of that delivery of yours first. Trust me, I know Rinascita like the back of my hand.","quest_name":"Mummer's Wish","quest_id":119800000},{"text":"These sigils refer to four different locations. But since Septimont City relocated uphill a while back, so too did the people who used to live there.","quest_name":"Mummer's Wish","quest_id":119800000},{"text":"Don't worry, I'll help you locate these Melody Box recipients.","quest_name":"Mummer's Wish","quest_id":119800000},{"text":"They should have all moved close to the hilltop Resonance Beacon. It'll be easy. Shall we?","quest_name":"Mummer's Wish","quest_id":119800000},{"text":"The third recipient lives here.","quest_name":"Mummer's Wish","quest_id":119800000},{"text":"They're quite a renowned family in Septimont. Their eldest son, Galba, is a veteran of the Hunter's Den.","quest_name":"Mummer's Wish","quest_id":119800000},{"text":"I sent them a message to let them know we were coming, but they never replied… Please don't tell me this is going to be like the last two recipients...","quest_name":"Mummer's Wish","quest_id":119800000},{"text":"Don't you worry. Journalists move fast and are hard to hit.","quest_name":"Mummer's Wish","quest_id":119800000},{"text":"Wait, the door's opening. A medic. I'll go talk to her and see what I can find.","quest_name":"Mummer's Wish","quest_id":119800000},{"text":"Strozzia… Strozzia… Now that we have her name, it makes things easy. I know basically everyone in Ragunna.","quest_name":"Mummer's Wish","quest_id":119800000},{"text":"Excuse me?! Does this Echo of yours specialize in words that inflict emotional damage, {PlayerName}?","quest_name":"Mummer's Wish","quest_id":119800000},{"text":"My apologies, I don't usually talk to coffee machines or phonographs.","quest_name":"Mummer's Wish","quest_id":119800000},{"text":"Give me a second. My colleague in Ragunna just replied! They've found the address of the Strozzia residence. They never moved.","quest_name":"Mummer's Wish","quest_id":119800000},{"text":"Journalist's hidden ability. A trade secret. Anyway, let's go visit Ms. Strozzia's family.","quest_name":"Mummer's Wish","quest_id":119800000},{"text":"If we waste any more time, the Aria Mummer will be sent back to the Resonance Nexus.","quest_name":"Mummer's Wish","quest_id":119800000},{"text":"The Echo wasn't following orders from its master. It acted on its own, traveling from the Hunter's Den to Septimont City to make the deliveries, then back to Ragunna…","quest_name":"Mummer's Wish","quest_id":119800000},{"text":"It's remarkable. I wonder if Echoes really have feelings of their own.","quest_name":"Mummer's Wish","quest_id":119800000},{"text":"Echoes that the Blessed Maiden grew up with still worried about her even after being corrupted by the Dark Tide… Incredible, indeed.","quest_name":"Mummer's Wish","quest_id":119800000},{"text":"Echoes that thought they had been abandoned by their masters, yet still traveled to the farthest islands to find them… Incredible, indeed.","quest_name":"Mummer's Wish","quest_id":119800000},{"text":"Well, I'm not saying I don't believe your story. I've even seen a talking Echo with my own eyes, after all.","quest_name":"Mummer's Wish","quest_id":119800000},{"text":"It's just… I suddenly get this feeling that this vast world I see might only be a tiny corner of an infinite universe.","quest_name":"Mummer's Wish","quest_id":119800000},{"text":"I'm planning to write an article about Strozzia and her team. And, of course, about her Echo.","quest_name":"Mummer's Wish","quest_id":119800000},{"text":"It'll take some time, so you'd better not forget the exclusive interview you promised me!","quest_name":"Mummer's Wish","quest_id":119800000},{"text":"Great. I knew our Laureate wouldn't go back on {Male=his;Female=her} word.","quest_name":"Mummer's Wish","quest_id":119800000},{"text":"I knew it! Don't you forget about it! I'll come find you once I'm done!","quest_name":"Mummer's Wish","quest_id":119800000},{"text":"I've got work on this article now. Until next time! Don't forget to fit me into your busy schedule!","quest_name":"Mummer's Wish","quest_id":119800000}]}